Breathing through the legs is extremely useful for relieving fatigue, especially when standing or walking for a long time, as well as for varicose veins.
<p> Breathing through the hands helps to increase the sensitivity of the palms which makes it possible to diagnose and treat with the hands.
<p> In addition these exercises help to execute retransmit and emit the right kind of qi including for the treatment of patients. The same method of breathing allows you to remove pain from your body, for example, when having bruises.